description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Jemboree is a match three game with interesting and unique game mechanics. Instead of finding matches on an already filled board, you create the combinations yourself. Have a fun relaxing time playing Zen mode, or challenge yourself, and the clock, and take on Time-Attack mode for a real test of skill.
